Abstract = {This research investigates the application of artificial intelligence
   (AI) tools to enhance engineering education. It examines how AI
   facilitates personalized learning through intelligent tutoring systems
   and adaptive platforms and explores its role in virtual laboratories and
   curriculum design. Practical applications are demonstrated through an
   experiential analysis of various AI tools, ranging from general
   conceptualization platforms to specialized multimedia creation software.
   The study also explores AI ` s capacity to streamline student assessment
   via digital and handwritten analysis, and rubric generation. The
   findings highlight AI ` s potential to create dynamic and efficient
   educational frameworks, emphasizing the need for responsible integration
   to maximize its impact on engineering education.},
